name: Filo Corp
longDescription: Filo Mining Corp is a Canada-based mineral exploration company engaged in the acquisition, exploration and development of mineral properties in South America. The company is focused on the Filo del Sol Project which is comprised of two adjacent landholdings, the Filo del Sol Property located in San Juan Province, Argentina, and the Tamberias Property, located in Region III, Chile.
